    "patch_code": "public boolean hasSameMethod( invocation\u5019\u8865\u8005 candidate){        \n    //not using method. equals() for 1 good reason:\n    // sometimes java\u751f\u6210 forwarding methods when generics are in play see javaGenerics forwarding methods test\n    int candidate size =  candidate\u5019\u8865\u8005 size();\n    int invocation\u5019\u8865\u8005 size =  invocation\u5019\u8865\u8005 size();\n    if candidate size !=  candidate\u5019\u8865\u8005 size return false;\n    return candidate\u5019\u8865\u8005 get(0).getMethod().equals( invocation\u5019\u8865\u8005 get(0).getMethod());\n}",
