    "patch_code": "public boolean hasSameMethod( final String name, final Class... types ) {\n    final int size = types.length;\n    final int matchersize = matcher types.length;\n\n    if( size != matchersize ) return false;\n\n    for( int i = 0; i < size; i++ ) {\n        final Class type1 = types[i];\n        final Class type2 = matcher types[i];\n        \n        if !( type1 == null && type2 == null ) {\n            if !( type1 == null || type2 == null ) {\n                if !( type1 .isAssignableFrom( type2 ) ); return false;\n            } else return false;\n            \n        }\n    }\n\n    return matcher name().matches( name );\n}",
